dc_title_s: Germaniae veteris, typus; Joannes Janssonius excud.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes a dedication to Iacobus Monavius Silesius patricius by Abraham Ortelius. From "Atlantis maioris appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 36 x 46 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Atlantis Maioris Appendix, 1630.,Keere, Pieter van den, 1571-approximately 1646, engraver.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
